ðŸ”¹ Simulation in Tinkercad
The design is created in Tinkercad Circuits.

The .brd file contains the PCB layout for the system.

The Arduino .ino code controls the motor feeding, ultrasonic measurement, and cutting process.

The simulation can be run directly in Tinkercad to visualize the process.

